        "Air Quality &#8594; Arthritis": "Women living within 50 meters of a major road or interstate in the United States are at a 31% increased risk of rheumatoid arthritis compared with women living more than 200 meters away from major roadways (<a href=\"https://awseastaging.epa.gov/EcoHealthBrowser/bibliography.html#Hart_2009\" target=\"_blank\">Hart et al., 2009</a>; n=90,297, USA). ",
